Product Manufacturer Ratings by EnergySage




Product Manufacturer Ratings by EnergySage
Learn More


Learn More




Overall Rating:  Standard


• At or better than industry average performance, quality, and durability specifications
• Industry average warranty coverage



Warranty Rating:  Standard


• Standard-level performance output and materials warranties



Performance Quality Durability Rating:  Standard


• Efficiency: All of REC Solar's panel models operate within the industry average efficiency range
• Power output: REC Solar's internal testing indicates that their panels are capable of producing at least as much power as their power output rating
• Temperature sensitivity: All of REC Solar's panel models are less sensitive to high temperatures than the industry average
• Quality manufacturing standards: Compliant
• Durability standards: Compliant
• Snow & wind load: Snow and wind load ratings are below industry average






Product Manufacturing Details




Product Manufacturing Details



Current Models And Output
REC 240PE BLK 240W, REC 245PE 245W, REC240PE 240W, REC245PE 245W


Product Technology
Polycrystalline


Efficiency
14.5-16.1%


Product warranty duration
10 Years


What's Covered in Product Warranty
REC Solar's product warranty covers defects in material and workmanship within a period of 10 (ten) years.


Product performance warranty
At the end of 25 Years power output should be no less than 80.2%.


What's covered in performance warranty
REC Solar's performance warranty covers the output efficiency of your solar system. After a period of 25 (twenty-five) years output should be no less than 80.2%. Each module will have an output of 97% within the first year of purchase. The maximum degradation of the module will be no more than 0.7% each year. If the output is reduced to less than 80.2% in 25 years or the degradation rate exceeds 0.7% annually REC Solar will repair or replace the defective module(s).   


Where Manufactured?
Singapore


Corporate/Ownership Structure
Private Subsidiary of Renewable Energy Corporation ASA






